  Adele, 34, wowed in the curve-hugging, off the shoulder gown for the ceremony, which was held at the New York Public Library. Her dress featured a flattering sweetheart neckline and tulle sleeves. She wore her blonde hair in loose waves and finished off her look with some black pointed heels, which had silver soles underneath. The singer and her sports agent partner Rich, 40, posed for pictures with famous NBA star Lebron James and his wife Savannah.   